---
title: One-Pot Beefy Taco Soup with Mexican Cheese & Sour Cream
description: A soup that tastes like tacos but is even easier to make? It’s not a culinary fantasy. This hearty, zesty soup is the real deal! Ground beef is cooked with warming spices then simmered with beans in a creamy tomato broth. Just like tacos, each bowl is finished with your favorite fixings:a sprinkle of Mexican cheese, cool dollop of sour cream, and a bright flurry of scallions. Grab your big spoon for this one, folks!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/one-pot-beefy-taco-soup-436db38a.jpg
